Feature: Department Views # features/department_views.feature:1

  Scenario: View employees in "Customer Service" department            # features/department_views.feature:2
    Given the following employees exist                                # None
      | first_name | last_name | department_id |
      | Alice      | Smith     | 1             |
      | Bob        | Johnson   | 2             |
      | Carol      | Williams  | 1             |
    When I visit "/departments/1/employees/"                           # None
    Then I should see 2 employees                                      # None
    And I should see "Alice Smith" in the results                      # None
    And I should see "Carol Williams" in the results                   # None
    But I should not see "Bob Johnson"                                 # None
    And the response should contain department name "Customer Service" # None

